# Whitelist approach: deny everything at root, then allow specific items.
# Keeps business/internal docs local, only the website and its CHANGELOG ship to this repo.

/*
!.gitignore
!.github/
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!DEPLOY.md
!KOLTON-FEEDBACK-CHANGES.md
!site/

# Deny common junk anywhere
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.cache/
**/__pycache__/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/credentials*
**/secrets*
